            "title": "Neutrophils express the high affinity receptor for IgG (Fc gamma RI, CD64) after in vivo application of recombinant human granulocyte colony-stimulating factor.",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "R",
