            "title": "Integrating Signals from IFN-γ and IL-4 by B Cells: Positive and Negative Effects on CD40 Ligand-Induced Proliferation, Survival, and Division-Linked Isotype Switching to IgG1, IgE and IgG2a",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
