            "title": "A comprehensive comparison of RNA-Seq-based transcriptome analysis from reads to differential gene expression and cross-comparison with microarrays: A case study in Saccharomyces cerevisiae",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Intawat",
